title: Is Texas Better Than LA? Our Thoughts! Feat. Dror
description:
Hi everyone! 


So the question is, is Texas better than LA? In today's episode, my friend, Dror, and I will talk all about it from our personal experiences. 

Want to make an appearance on Happy and Healthy? Send in a voice message! We will then play and respond to it on our next episode.


Follow us!
